race.comment: LAKOTA COURTNEY (3) boasts a strong record this journey here with four wins and four minors from 10 tries. Scored by a neck last time (17.62) in a Grade 5 over 324m at this track. Makes strong appeal on best. GO FORWARD SPOT (2) shapes well after a fast run last time, finishing third in a Grade 5 at this track in 17.69. Harder here but expected to feature again. CHA CHA ETHICS (7) boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten a neck (17.64) behind LAKOTA COURTNEY at this track. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Overdue and gets her chance. SMART MINX (8) is among the chances again if she runs up to the latest effort.
